div.p:
HOW terrible will the Judgment of GOD be to the
Wicked! CHRIST, whom they have outrageouſly abus'd, is to give Sentence;
their own Conſciences to be Witneſs againſt them, and the Devil waits
for the word of Command to put it in Execution. No Grace now to be hoped for;
no room left for Repentance.
